				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The ox is waiting in the cave while the tieflings decide whether to return to the road or not. He has been watching the druids in the grove below, and how they can change into any form they wish. He's wistful and sulky, wishing he could change his own shape from an ox to something less subservient.\r\n\r\nHe can give us a hint about an item stashed in his hay."
				}
